name: Gajanan Tiles
overview:
Established in the year 1985, at Pune, Maharashtra (India), we, “Gajanan Tiles” are recognized as the leading Manufacturer and Supplier of a quality assured gamut of Designer Concrete Tiles, Designer Concrete Block, Glossing Tiles - Wall Mount, Glossy Tiles and Glossy Paving Blocks such as 3D Tiles, Monarch Pyramid, Falcon, Stone, Dollar, Clock, Bubbles Tiles, Plain Brick, Curve Brick, etc.

Client Satisfaction: Our organization is a client oriented and lays great emphasis on the achievement of the highest level of the client’s satisfaction. By offering an unmatched quality range of Designer Concrete Tiles, Designer Concrete Block, Glossing Tiles - Wall Mount, Glossy Tiles and Glossy Paving Blocks to our clients, We offer our products in customized forms, which are designed according to the client’s requirements.

Our Team: Our organization supported by a team of experienced professionals, who assist us in the proper maintenance of our infrastructure facility. We have recruited our team on the basis of their skills and vast industry experience who are highly dedicated towards our organization.

Quality Standards: Quality is considered as one of the most important factors of our organization. We believe in maintaining long-term business relationships with our customers. Our conformation to stern quality standards that comply with the international parameters, have aided us to maintain stability in each batch of products offered by us.

Why Us?: Competitive rates Prompt and timely service Good quality products Client will benefit with service support provided by group of professionals Customized services Effective and agile customer service and delivery Cost effective services
